2006;;The Secret Life of Happy People;;Canadian;;Stéphane Lapointe;;Gilbert Sicotte, Marc Paquet, Catherine de Léan, Marie Gignac;;comedy, drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Secret_Life_of_Happy_People;;Thomas Dufresne (Paquet) is the black sheep of his bourgeois family. One day, he meets a free-spirited waitress named Audrey (Catherine Deléan) who changes his life. Thomas eventually finds out the truth behind their seemingly innocent encounter, which may change his family forever.